<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Relatório de Análise - {{asset.ticker}}</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            color: #1f2937;
            line-height: 1.6;
            background-color: #ffffff;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 210mm;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        /* Header */
        .header {
            border-bottom: 3px solid #2563eb;
            padding-bottom: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .header-top {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .logo {
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #2563eb;
        }

        .report-date {
            text-align: right;
            color: #6b7280;
            font-size: 12px;
        }

        .header-title {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #111827;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }

        .header-subtitle {
            color: #6b7280;
            font-size: 14px;
            margin-top: 5px;
        }

        /* Asset Info */
        .asset-info {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f3f4f6 0%, #e5e7eb 100%);
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .asset-header {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: flex-start;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .asset-name {
            flex: 1;
        }

        .asset-ticker {
            font-size: 32px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #111827;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }

        .asset-full-name {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #6b7280;
        }

        .asset-price {
            text-align: right;
        }

        .price-label {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #6b7280;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }

        .price-value {
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #111827;
        }

        .price-change {
            font-size: 14px;
            margin-top: 5px;
        }

        .price-change.positive {
            color: #16a34a;
        }

        .price-change.negative {
            color: #dc2626;
        }

        /* Recommendation Box */
        .recommendation-box {
            display: flex;
            gap: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .recommendation-card {
            flex: 1;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            border: 2px solid #e5e7eb;
        }

        .recommendation-card.main {
            background: {{recommendationColor}};
            color: white;
            border-color: {{recommendationColor}};
        }

        .card-label {
            font-size: 12px;
            opacity: 0.9;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
        }

        .card-value {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .card-info {
            font-size: 12px;
            margin-top: 8px;
            opacity: 0.8;
        }

        /* Summary Section */
        .section {
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            page-break-inside: avoid;
        }

        .section-title {
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #111827;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            padding-bottom: 8px;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #e5e7eb;
        }

        .section-content {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #374151;
            line-height: 1.8;
        }

        /* Analysis Data */
        .analysis-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
            gap: 15px;
            margin-top: 15px;
        }

        .analysis-item {
            background: #f9fafb;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
        }

        .analysis-item-label {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #6b7280;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }

        .analysis-item-value {
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #111827;
        }

        /* Data Sources */
        .data-sources {
            background: #eff6ff;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            border-left: 4px solid #2563eb;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        .data-sources-title {
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #1e40af;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        .data-sources-list {
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #1e3a8a;
        }

        /* Footer */
        .footer {
            margin-top: 50px;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
            font-size: 11px;
            color: #6b7280;
        }

        .disclaimer {
            background: #fef3c7;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            border-left: 4px solid #f59e0b;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .disclaimer-title {
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #92400e;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }

        .disclaimer-text {
            color: #78350f;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .footer-info {
            text-align: center;
            line-height: 1.8;
        }

        /* Print Styles */
        @media print {
            body {
                print-color-adjust: exact;
                -webkit-print-color-adjust: exact;
            }

            .section {
                page-break-inside: avoid;
            }
        }

        /* Helper Classes */
        .mb-10 {
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .mb-20 {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .text-center {
            text-align: center;
        }

        .text-muted {
            color: #6b7280;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <!-- Header -->
        <div class="header">
            <div class="header-top">
                <div class="logo">B3 AI Analysis</div>
                <div class="report-date">
                    <div>Gerado em</div>
                    <div><strong>{{formattedDate}}</strong></div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="header-title">Relatório de Análise de Investimento</div>
            <div class="header-subtitle">Análise Completa com Inteligência Artificial</div>
        </div>

        <!-- Asset Info -->
        <div class="asset-info">
            <div class="asset-header">
                <div class="asset-name">
                    <div class="asset-ticker">{{asset.ticker}}</div>
                    <div class="asset-full-name">{{asset.name}}</div>
                    <div class="asset-full-name text-muted">
                        {{#if asset.sector}}{{asset.sector}}{{/if}}
                        {{#if asset.subsector}} • {{asset.subsector}}{{/if}}
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="asset-price">
                    <div class="price-label">Preço Atual</div>
                    <div class="price-value">{{formattedPrice}}</div>
                    {{#if changePercent}}
                    <div class="price-change {{#if (eq changePercent 0)}}{{else}}{{#if (gt changePercent 0)}}positive{{else}}negative{{/if}}{{/if}}">
                        {{formattedChangePercent}}
                    </div>
                    {{/if}}
                    {{#if currentPriceDate}}
                    <div class="price-label" style="margin-top: 5px;">{{formatDate currentPriceDate}}</div>
                    {{/if}}
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Recommendation & Confidence -->
        <div class="recommendation-box">
            <div class="recommendation-card main">
                <div class="card-label">Recomendação</div>
                <div class="card-value">{{recommendationLabel}}</div>
                <div class="card-info">Baseado em análise multi-fonte</div>
            </div>
            <div class="recommendation-card">
                <div class="card-label">Nível de Confiança</div>
                <div class="card-value" style="color: {{recommendationColor}};">{{confidencePercent}}</div>
                <div class="card-info">{{analysis.sourcesCount}} fonte(s) validada(s)</div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Summary Section -->
        {{#if analysis.summary}}
        <div class="section">
            <div class="section-title">Resumo Executivo</div>
            <div class="section-content">
                {{analysis.summary}}
            </div>
        </div>
        {{/if}}

        <!-- Fundamental Analysis -->
        {{#if analysis.analysis}}
        <div class="section">
            <div class="section-title">Análise Fundamentalista</div>
            <div class="analysis-grid">
                {{#if analysis.analysis.pl}}
                <div class="analysis-item">
                    <div class="analysis-item-label">P/L (Preço/Lucro)</div>
                    <div class="analysis-item-value">{{formatNumber analysis.analysis.pl}}</div>
                </div>
                {{/if}}
                {{#if analysis.analysis.pvp}}
                <div class="analysis-item">
                    <div class="analysis-item-label">P/VP (Preço/Valor Patrimonial)</div>
                    <div class="analysis-item-value">{{formatNumber analysis.analysis.pvp}}</div>
                </div>
                {{/if}}
                {{#if analysis.analysis.roe}}
                <div class="analysis-item">
                    <div class="analysis-item-label">ROE (Retorno sobre Patrimônio)</div>
                    <div class="analysis-item-value">{{formatPercent analysis.analysis.roe}}</div>
                </div>
                {{/if}}
                {{#if analysis.analysis.dividendYield}}
                <div class="analysis-item">
                    <div class="analysis-item-label">Dividend Yield</div>
                    <div class="analysis-item-value">{{formatPercent analysis.analysis.dividendYield}}</div>
                </div>
                {{/if}}
                {{#if analysis.analysis.lpa}}
                <div class="analysis-item">
                    <div class="analysis-item-label">LPA (Lucro por Ação)</div>
                    <div class="analysis-item-value">R$ {{formatNumber analysis.analysis.lpa}}</div>
                </div>
                {{/if}}
                {{#if analysis.analysis.vpa}}
                <div class="analysis-item">
                    <div class="analysis-item-label">VPA (Valor Patrimonial por Ação)</div>
                    <div class="analysis-item-value">R$ {{formatNumber analysis.analysis.vpa}}</div>
                </div>
                {{/if}}
                {{#if analysis.analysis.ebitda}}
                <div class="analysis-item">
                    <div class="analysis-item-label">EBITDA</div>
                    <div class="analysis-item-value">R$ {{formatNumber analysis.analysis.ebitda}}</div>
                </div>
                {{/if}}
                {{#if analysis.analysis.margemLiquida}}
                <div class="analysis-item">
                    <div class="analysis-item-label">Margem Líquida</div>
                    <div class="analysis-item-value">{{formatPercent analysis.analysis.margemLiquida}}</div>
                </div>
                {{/if}}
            </div>
        </div>
        {{/if}}

        <!-- Risks -->
        {{#if risks}}
        <div class="section">
            <div class="section-title">Análise de Riscos</div>
            <div class="section-content">
                {{#each risks}}
                <div class="mb-10">
                    <strong>{{this.type}}:</strong> {{this.description}}
                </div>
                {{/each}}
            </div>
        </div>
        {{/if}}

        <!-- Data Sources -->
        {{#if analysis.dataSources}}
        <div class="data-sources">
            <div class="data-sources-title">Fontes de Dados Utilizadas</div>
            <div class="data-sources-list">
                {{#each analysis.dataSources}}
                • {{this}}{{#unless @last}}, {{/unless}}
                {{/each}}
            </div>
        </div>
        {{/if}}

        <!-- Footer -->
        <div class="footer">
            <div class="disclaimer">
                <div class="disclaimer-title">⚠️ Aviso Legal</div>
                <div class="disclaimer-text">
                    Este relatório foi gerado automaticamente por inteligência artificial e tem caráter meramente informativo.
                    Não constitui recomendação de investimento, oferta ou solicitação para compra ou venda de valores mobiliários.
                    O investidor é responsável por suas próprias decisões de investimento e deve buscar orientação profissional
                    quando necessário. Rentabilidade passada não garante resultados futuros.
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="footer-info">
                <div><strong>B3 AI Analysis Platform</strong></div>
                <div>Plataforma de Análise de Investimentos com Inteligência Artificial</div>
                <div style="margin-top: 10px;">Documento ID: {{analysis.id}}</div>
                <div>Gerado em {{formattedDate}}</div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
